{"tid":1243323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一名國中生向韓國瑜說：「你要去選總統這件事情，真的太可笑，不要讓你的感性壓過你的理性。」","createTime":"2019-06-19T11:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T16:07:35.000Z","uid":35790,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"428468c8544a1d73429b019a0a8e61d4337c88c8","tid":1243323,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"國中生當面說「選總統很可笑」 韓國瑜：表達己見勇氣可嘉<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-19<br />\n<br />\n高雄市長韓國瑜今天下午到社教館，與優良畢業生市長獎、模範生合影。一名獲模範生獎的國中男生，<span style=\"color: red;\">拍照時向市長說，「覺得韓市長選總統很可笑，醒一醒不要讓感性壓過你的理性。」</span>韓國瑜事後受訪時表示尊重學生，15歲就敢把心中的想法表達出來很好，台灣是自由民主的社會，大家都可以表述心中意見。<br />\n<br />\n這名學生跟韓市長說：「你要去選總統這件事情，真的太可笑，不要讓你的感性，壓過你的理性。」學生請市長醒一醒，既然選前做了這麼多承諾，現在又要去選總統，當然對名譽也有點不太好的地方，況且也做了一些承諾、政見之類的，也不是這麼有道理。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">場外一名女學生說，如果市長兌現承諾，我就會喜歡他，但沒有做到承諾。媒體追問是什麼承諾？女學生說：「就是發大財啊！」</span><br />\n<br />\n因為拍照時間非常短，後面等待的隊伍還很長，當下市長是笑一笑，拍拍學生肩膀。市長韓國瑜在拍照現場外受訪時稱讚這名男受獎人，非常好，國中三年級就敢把心中的想法表達出來，應給予尊重。<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜說，很多高雄市民朋友對此心中也是矛盾的，都給予尊重。台灣是自由民主的社會，大家都可以表述心中意見，15歲的學生願意表達己見，勇氣可嘉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3880958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F3880958&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=22db84a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6656/3880958</a>"},{"pid":"d279fbbf873949dc8e8ce7b9aadc817a3df68149","tid":1243323,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T11:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e790fc0fbb353f856e526f72d48487ec0101d0","tid":1243323,"uid":55960,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"就是發大財啊！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5359e58264f13ce28b29b9930103a5e2830e5f","tid":1243323,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64e790fc0fbb353f856e526f72d48487ec0101d0","tid":1243323,"uid":55960,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"就是發大財啊！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好醒"},{"pid":"d84138b382e128e02b7a249c6f88c69495080ad6","tid":1243323,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"64e790fc0fbb353f856e526f72d48487ec0101d0","tid":1243323,"uid":55960,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T15:42:30.000Z","msg":"就是發大財啊！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=OJEezQlNQGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOJEezQlNQGI&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=c9257cf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=OJEezQlNQGI</a>"},{"pid":"0e1cdeb47a9ecbc7bb7bee9b5398ee0a2099b1e5","tid":1243323,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:07:35.000Z","msg":"模範生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}